title: Seattle Seahawks-Carolina Panthers: Live updates, score and game chat
text:
Russell Wilson and the Seattle Seahawks kick off Week 6 of the 2015 NFL season with a trip home to CenturyLink Field where they will host Cam Newton and the Carolina Panthers on Sunday.
More : TV channel and how to watch this game online
Follow along as we bring you live updates and analysis from the game from kickoff through the final whistle in the comments section below. Have thoughts on how coach Pete Carroll and the Seahawks are performing? Don't hesitate to jump in on the live updates and chat with us as the game rolls along.
